# Chiara AI Consulting Website

## Live Website
https://chiaraaiconsulting.se

## Overview
This project is the official website for Chiara AI Consulting. It is designed to present AI-driven consulting services, solutions, and client engagement capabilities.

The application is a production-ready web solution deployed with a custom domain.

## Features
- Responsive modern user interface
- AI consulting service pages
- Contact and lead generation functionality
- Chatbot integration
- Clean and user-friendly design

## Tech Stack
- React (Vite)
- TypeScript
- Tailwind CSS
- shadcn-ui
- Supabase
- Lovable (builder and hosting)

## DevOps and Engineering Practices
- Version control using GitHub
- Continuous updates through Lovable synchronization
- Structured frontend architecture
- Deployment with a custom production domain

